div.span: Resets the target's evasion to normal and prevents any further boosting until the target leaves the field. A ghost under this effect takes normal damage from normal and fighting moves. This move itself ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.

Inflicts regular damage. User is forced to use this move for 25 turns, selected at random. All Pokmon on the field wake up, and none can fall to sleep until the lock-in ends.
Pokmon cannot use rest during this effect.
This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
